events.text: Welcome to your new league!
The Nets traded Jason Collins, Anthony Johnson, Reggie Slater, and a 2002 1st round pick (NJN) to the Mavericks for Tim Hardaway.
The Nets traded Keith Van Horn to the Mavericks for Juwan Howard.
The Nets traded Tim Hardaway and Juwan Howard to the Mavericks for Jason Collins, Anthony Johnson, Reggie Slater, Keith Van Horn, and a 2002 1st round pick (NJN).
The Mavericks traded Tim Hardaway, Johnny Newman, a 2003 2nd round pick (DAL), and a 2005 2nd round pick (DAL) to the Wizards for Michael Jordan and Chris Whitney.
The Nets traded Brandon Armstrong, Jason Collins, and Anthony Johnson to the Pistons for Chucky Atkins.
The Jazz traded John Amaechi and John Stockton to the Lakers for Joe Crispin, Mike Penberthy, Mitch Richmond, and a 2005 2nd round pick (LAL).
The Nets traded Derrick Dial, Richard Jefferson, Reggie Slater, Aaron Williams, a 2004 2nd round pick (NJN), and a 2006 2nd round pick (NJN) to the Rockets for Cuttino Mobley.
The Nets traded a 2005 2nd round pick (NJN) to the Pistons for nothing.
The Timberwolves traded Rasho Nesterović, Joe Smith, a 2005 1st round pick (MIN), and a 2006 1st round pick (MIN) to the Bulls for Brad Miller.
